---
title: Zahtar Cod With Balsamic Bulgur
description: We love good Zahtar Cod With Balsamic Bulgur and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/zahtar-cod-e673d92b-852ff9f4.jpg
